Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙 到底打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经阻止过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的话不就是万事大吉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连救援活动都没展开而被卷入的小琳她们也是受害者…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看GGP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动暂时中止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员把这次事件给忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个字都不准泄露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙由我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌成这样是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是在害怕GGP和警察
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他动摇了的是Fuego？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:04.34,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:04.34,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:47.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:47.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:51.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:51.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:13.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:13.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
